OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy across Scotland
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain and
OL,7,Fthunderstorms, accompanied by hail and
OL,8,Fgusty winds. Elsewhere, some early
OL,9,Fshowers, then dry with sunny spells.
OL,10,FExtreme heat transferring to eastern
OL,11,FEngland, with temperatures further
OL,12,Fwest dropping slightly.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain slowly clearing
OL,15,FScotland. Heavy, possibly thundery,
OL,16,Fshowers cross the southeast in the
OL,17,Fsecond half of the night. Dry with
OL,18,Fclear spells elsewhere. Warm, but
OL,19,Fslightly cooler than previous nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
