OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FShowers, possibly thundery,
OL,6,Fin the east and southeast. Rain slowly
OL,7,Fedging into the northwest. Sunny
OL,8,Fspells elsewhere. Still hot in the
OL,9,Fsoutheast, but temperatures lower than
OL,10,Fof late.
